{"version":1,"entries":{"person_1245069_translations":{"at":1773688717179,"data":{"id":1245069,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Go Hyun-jung (Hangul: 고현정; born March 2, 1971) is a South  Korean actress. She debuted in the entertainment scene as a Miss  Korea runner-up in 1989 and went on to star in Sandglass, one of the  highest-rated and critically acclaimed dramas in Korean television  history. She retired after marrying chaebol Chung Yong-jin in 1995, then  returned to acting after their divorce in 2003. Go has since regained  her top star status in Korea, becoming the highest paid actress on TV  after the success of her series Queen Seondeok and Daemul.","name":"Ko Hyun-jung","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"고현정","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"高贤廷","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"高賢貞","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"高賢廷","primary":false}}]}},"person_2252989_translations":{"at":1773688719989,"data":{"id":2252989,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Katy M. O'Brian (born February 12, 1989) is an American actress.\n\nShe is best known for her roles as bodybuilder Jackie in Love Lies Bleeding, Imperial communications officer Elia Kane in the second and third seasons of The Mandalorian, George in Syfy's zombie show Z Nation, Major Sara Grey in The CW's superhero series Black Lightning, Kimball in Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D., and Jentorra in Ant-Man and the Wasp: Quantumania.","name":"Katy O'Brian","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"케이티 M. 오브라이언","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"Katy M. O’Brian ist eine US-amerikanische Schauspielerin und Kampfsportlerin. O’Brian war das erste Mal im Jahr 2012 in einer kleinen Rolle im Film Student Seven vor der Kamera zu sehen. Danach folgten Engagements für einige Kurzfilme. 2017 und 2018 trat sie in einer kleinen Rolle in The Walking Dead auf. 2018 gehörte sie zur Hauptbesetzung der fünften Staffel der Serie Z Nation. Ein Jahr später wurde sie als Major Sara Grey für die Serie Black Lightning besetzt, in der sie bis 2020 zu sehen war. Es folgten Gastrollen in Westworld, Marvel’s Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D., The Mandalorian, Magnum P.I. und The Rookie. 2023 war sie als Rebellenführerin Jentorra in einer Nebenrolle in der Marvel-Verfilmung Ant-Man and the Wasp: Quantumania zu sehen.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"Katy M. O'Brian, née le 12 février 1989 à Indianapolis, est une actrice, écrivaine et artiste martiale américaine.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"凱蒂·奧布萊恩","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Кэти О'Брайан","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"凯蒂·奥布莱恩（Katy M. O'Brian，1989年2月12日-），美国女演员、作家、武术家。她最出名的角色是在《蚁人与黄蜂女：量子狂潮》中饰演詹托拉，在 Syfy 的僵尸节目《Z Nation》中饰演乔治，在 CW 的超级英雄系列《黑色闪电》中饰演莎拉·格雷少校，在漫威的《神盾局特工》中饰演金博尔。她在《曼达洛人》的第二季和第三季中扮演帝国通讯官埃利亚·凯恩。","name":"凯蒂·M·奥布莱恩","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","en